title: Talkin' 'Bout Your Generation
overview: Hosted by Shaun Micallef, Talkin' 'Bout Your Generation is an hour-long quiz show testing the popular culture knowledge of teams from three different cultural generations. The generation team captains are Amanda Keller (Baby Boomers), Charlie Pickering (Generation X) and Josh Thomas (Generation Y).The show ended on Network Ten in 2012 but has been revived by the Nine Network with 6 new episodes set to air in 2018. The new generation captains are Robyn Butler (Generation X) Andy Lee (Generation Y) and Laurence Boxhall (Generation Z). Shaun Micallef will again host the show.
